"""Test get_fe_port_metrics."""
response = self.perf.get_fe_port_metrics(start_date=self.time_now, end_date
    =self.time_now, director_id=self.p_data.fe_dir_id, metriclist=pc.KPI,
    port_id=self.p_data.fe_port_id, dataformat=pc.AVERAGE)
self.assertIsInstance(response, dict)
self.assertTrue(response)
self.assertEqual(len(response.get('result')), 2)
